        "title": "fix(ui): rename chat sessions from the picker",
        "body": "## Summary\r\n- add inline session-title rename controls to the chat session picker/sidebar using the existing `sessions.patch` label contract\r\n- preserve picker state around rename by blocking conflicting actions during save, keeping close behavior predictable, and refreshing the picker/session lists without dropping loaded pages\r\n- localize the new rename error messages through the Control UI i18n path\r\n- add focused chat picker tests for rename open/save/no-op/in-flight cases\r\n\r\nCloses #89922.\r\n\r\n## Verification\r\n- `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs ui/src/ui/views/chat.test.ts`\r\n- `.agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode local`\r\n- `git diff --check`\r\n\r\n## Real behavior proof\r\n- Behavior addressed: Chat/sidebar session picker can now rename session titles inline instead of forcing users into the Sessions table.\r\n- Real environment tested: Real Chromium browser against the local Control UI app with a deterministic mocked Gateway transport.\r\n- Exact steps or command run after this patch: `node --import tsx .artifacts/control-ui-e2e/session-picker-rename-proof/record.mjs`\r\n- Evidence after fix: Local browser proof artifacts were captured under `.artifacts/control-ui-e2e/session-picker-rename-proof/`.\r\n- Observed result after fix: The picker opened, entered inline rename mode for `agent:main:work`, saved `Ops notes`, then reopened with the renamed title still visible.\r\n- Browser proof files:\r\n \r\n<img width=\"1280\" height=\"900\" alt=\"01-picker-open\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3d0f75e2-3ab2-4d7e-ae3f-6493127e1d8e\" />\r\n<img width=\"1280\" height=\"900\" alt=\"02-rename-editing\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c0baa1f5-a0d1-423f-90a1-429a49c3f440\" />\r\n<img width=\"1280\" height=\"900\" alt=\"03-rename-saved\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3634e733-f17c-4ac7-b92f-e693c52443de\" />\r\n<img width=\"1280\" height=\"900\" alt=\"04-rename-reopened\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/790e8f86-55e2-483f-9d01-43ca441ca8a5\" />\r\n[session-picker-rename.webm](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/5a7f19ab-f79d-4d80-8381-ff1eee2f7850)\r\n\r\n- What was not tested: Live remote Gateway/provider state; this proof uses a deterministic mocked Gateway to isolate the visible Control UI rename flow.\r\n",
